-- Brandt Snedeker Takes Lead From Scott in British Open
-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 2012-07-20T11:24:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-20/brandt-snedeker-takes-lead-from-scott-in-british-open.html
American Brandt Snedeker moved into
the lead at 7 under par during the second round of golf’s
British Open.  Snedeker has three birdies in his first seven holes today
at Royal Lytham & St. Annes in northwest England. He’s one
stroke better than Australia’s  Adam Scott , who shot a 6-under 64
yesterday. Scott tees off at 1:43 p.m. local time today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  